# OpenSSH Server Configuration
Port 22
Protocol 2

HostKeyAlgorithms ssh-ed25519,ecdsa-sha2-nistp256,rsa-sha2-512,rsa-sha2-256
KexAlgorithms curve25519-sha256,ecdh-sha2-nistp256,diffie-hellman-group16-sha512
Ciphers aes256-gcm@openssh.com,chacha20-poly1305@openssh.com,aes128-gcm@openssh.com
MACs hmac-sha2-512-etm@openssh.com,hmac-sha2-256-etm@openssh.com

PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
